2 types of test env

Permanent Test Enviorment : E-commerece website

Test infra - Advantages of test env - Snapshot and checkpoints:

On physical server : Easy to rollback using snapshot
Scaling of hardware : How many user it can handle or load 1 Processor to 4
Load testing to get good understanding of additional users.

Production in VM : Clone the Production Servers : Sensitive data should

Temp testing : Evaluate for 90 days to make final decision to buy.

Virtualization is good option : Turn up 1 new VM and install new accounting software

Go to public cloud : rather than buy new hardware for 3 months, rent a servers

AWS : monthly rates
EC2 spot instances : hourly rates .. for short testing 
